                                            "Age ${_getPartnerAge("${partnerListItemArray[index - 2]['partner_birth_date']}")}",
                                            style: TextStyle(
                                                color: AppColors.accentText,
                                                fontSize: 16,
                                                fontFamily: 'Barlow-Light'),
                                          )))
                                ])),
                        Container(),
                        Positioned(
                          top: 30,
                          right: 20,
